val schema = Encoders.product[Request].schema

val df = spark
    .read
    .option("header", "true")
    .schema(schema)
    .csv("/zeppelin/files/dataset.csv")
    .select($"uuid", $"origin", $"ip", toNav($"browser") as "browser", $"timestamp", $"latitude", $"longitude", $"price")
    .na.drop()
